OL,4,BDementia in football: Dawn Astle
OL,5,B'staggered' by head trauma research
OL,6, Former footballers who have suffered
OL,7, from dementia "must not be a
OL,8, statistic", says a prominent campaigner
OL,9, after research showed a link between
OL,10, the sport and the disease.
OL,12,FDawn Astle pushed for research after
OL,13,Fthe death of her father - ex-England
OL,14,Fstriker Jeff Astle - in 2002.
OL,16,FExperts have found ex-players are more
OL,17,Fthan three times more likely to die of
OL,18,Fdementia than people of the same age
OL,19,Frange in the general population.
OL,21,FAstle is "staggered" by the findings.
